    <note>Huang(2) Haoqian [844] His father, Xiaoxian [3415], moved from Jianning, Pucheng xian to Huaining, Yuanqiu xian. Guan's [849] grandson, Ziyou's [863] grandfather, Shi's [854] uncle (one source has father). Xiaoxian's great great grandson was Renrong [847], whose branch of the lineage moved to Shaowu, Shaowu xian at the beginning of the Southern Song. XCB, 257.4b, 308.5b; SHY:ZG, 66.12b. Still listed as a Pucheng jinshi in Fujian TZ, 147.19b. CBD, 4, 2895.</note>
